info.description:
MetaWall API 練習文件。<br>注意事項：登入成功後請點「Authorize」輸入 Token。<br><br>範例程式碼：<br><br>
```javascript
const config = {
  headers: { Authorization: token },
};
axios.post('/V2/api/user/check', {}, config)
  .then((res) => {
    console.log(res.data);
  })
  .catch((error) => {
    console.log(error.response.data);
  });
```
